OL,3,CChelsea to play all WSL games at
OL,4,CStamford Bridge from next season
OL,6,FChelsea will play all of their Women's
OL,7,FSuper League games at Stamford Bridge
OL,8,Ffrom next season and have already
OL,9,Fhosted their last competitive fixture
OL,10,Fat Kingsmeadow.
OL,12,FSonia Bompastor's side have played
OL,13,Fthree WSL games at the home of the
OL,14,Fclub's men's team so far this season
OL,15,Fand will round off their campaign
OL,16,Fthere against Manchester United in May.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
