CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776881467
OL,3,CChelsea to play all WSL games at
OL,4,CStamford Bridge from next season
OL,6,FThe upcoming FA Cup semi-final against
OL,7,FManchester City has been relocated to
OL,8,FStamford Bridge, meaning the dramatic
OL,9,F4-3 win over Aston Villa on March 29
OL,10,Fwas their final outing at the 4,850-
OL,11,Fcapacity ground in Kingston that has
OL,12,Fbeen their home since 2017.
OL,14,FA club statement said: "Stamford
OL,15,FBridge will give CFCW a stage
OL,16,Fbefitting the club's achievements and
OL,17,Fambition, a place to compete and win.
OL,26,@vD@XOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776881467
OL,3,CChelsea to play all WSL games at
OL,4,CStamford Bridge from next season
OL,6,F"This move reflects the club's
OL,7,Funwavering belief in the long-term
OL,8,Fopportunity in women's football as
OL,9,Fwell as the responsibility the club
OL,10,Fhas to help push the game forward.
OL,12,F"By establishing a permanent home at
OL,13,FStamford Bridge, CFCW is investing not
OL,14,Fjust in today but in a legacy.
OL,16,F"Playing at Stamford Bridge will
OL,17,Felevate visibility, provide
OL,18,Fconsistency for fans, unlock potential
OL,19,Fand inspire the next generation as the
OL,20,Fsport continues to grow."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
