CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776881467
OL,3,CChelsea to play all WSL games at
OL,4,CStamford Bridge from next season
OL,6,FIt is understood the move is motivated
OL,7,Fpartly by the potential for growing
OL,8,Fmatchday attendances and the greater
OL,9,Fcommercial possibilities offered by a
OL,10,Flarger, more developed stadium.
OL,12,FThere have been fluctuating
OL,13,Fattendances when the side have played
OL,14,Fat the club's main ground this season.
OL,15,FThe 2-0 defeat to Arsenal in January
OL,16,Fdrew a crowd of more than 30,000
OL,17,Fwhilst the win over London City
OL,18,FLionesses in November was watched by a
OL,19,Fcrowd of around 10,000.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776881467
OL,3,CChelsea to play all WSL games at
OL,4,CStamford Bridge from next season
OL,6,FBy contrast, Arsenal averaged 34,110
OL,7,Ffor their nine WSL fixtures at the
OL,8,FEmirates Stadium during the 2024-25
OL,9,Fseason, with more than 56,000 in
OL,10,Fattendance for their 5-0 win over
OL,11,FTottenham.
OL,13,FAn open letter from Chelsea's first-
OL,14,Fteam squad to supporters said: "This
OL,15,Fmoment is not just for us. It's for
OL,16,Fevery player to have worn the Chelsea
OL,17,Fbadge. It's for every person who has
OL,18,Fpushed the women's game forward. It's
OL,19,Ffor every supporter who has been with
OL,20,Fus on our incredible journey.
OL,26,@vD@`OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776881467
OL,3,CChelsea to play all WSL games at
OL,4,CStamford Bridge from next season
OL,6,F"This is a new chapter, but our
OL,7,Fambition remains the same. We want to
OL,8,Fwin. We want to lift more trophies. We
OL,9,Fwant to create further history. That
OL,10,Fis what Chelsea has always done ` and
OL,11,Fwe're going to continue that legacy
OL,12,Fwith our supporters beside us at the
OL,13,FBridge."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
