OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776881467
OL,3,CChelsea to play all WSL games at
OL,4,CStamford Bridge from next season
OL,6,FIt is hoped Chelsea will also be able
OL,7,Fto play Women's League Cup, FA Cup and
OL,8,F` pending qualification ` Champions
OL,9,FLeague fixtures at Stamford Bridge,
OL,10,Fthough scheduling around matches for
OL,11,Fthe men's side could lead to an
OL,12,Falternative ground being sought for
OL,13,Fsome cup games.
OL,15,FChelsea sold their women's team to a
OL,16,Fsubsidiary company, Chelsea FC Women
OL,17,F(CFCW), in 2024.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
