OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776881467
OL,3,CChelsea to play all WSL games at
OL,4,CStamford Bridge from next season
OL,6,FThe men's club recently released
OL,7,Faccounts for the year to June 2025
OL,8,Fwhich included a payment of #22.6m
OL,9,Ffrom CFCW, and sources close to the
OL,10,Fclub said almost #12m of that related
OL,11,Fto the sale of Kingsmeadow following
OL,12,Findependent valuation.
OL,14,FIt is understood that part of the deal
OL,15,Fthat saw the women's team set up as a
OL,16,Fstandalone business included an
OL,17,Fagreement with the men's side for
OL,18,FStamford Bridge to be used in exchange
OL,19,Ffor a service fee. Kingsmeadow will
OL,20,Fcontinue to host women's academy and
OL,21,Fage-group matches.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
